node.text: Hailed by golfing legends as having ‘the greatest golf courses in the world,’ @trumpturnberryscotland, @trumpdoonbeg, and @trumpscotland are must-visit destinations.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Trump Organization in Trump National Golf Club Bedminster with @trumpgolf, and @trumpgolfbedminster. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Taking in this incredible scene at @trumpgolfbedminster during the 38th Annual New Jersey Lottery Festival of Ballooning, accompanied by a stunning summer sunset.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by The Trump Organization on July 27, 2021 tagging @trumphotels, @trumpgolf, and @trumpscotland. May be an image of castle and outdoors.

node.text: Swipe to see our famed Clavis Whisky Bar at @trumpscotland’s MacLeod House, where a wee dram is a must during any visit, but especially on #NationalScotchDay.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by The Trump Organization on July 27, 2021 tagging @trumphotels, @trumpgolf, and @trumpscotland. May be an image of castle and outdoors.
Photo by The Trump Organization on July 27, 2021. May be an image of indoor.
Photo by The Trump Organization on July 27, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.
Photo shared by The Trump Organization on July 22, 2021 tagging @trumpwaikiki, and @trumphotels. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Experience the “Liquid Artistry of Wai‘olu” with a handcrafted specialty cocktail made from the finest and freshest local ingredients. Best enjoyed poolside at @trumpwaikiki.🍹

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by The Trump Organization on July 22, 2021 tagging @trumpwaikiki, and @trumphotels. May be an image of drink.
Photo by The Trump Organization on July 22, 2021. May be an image of pool.
Photo by The Trump Organization in Mar-a-Lago. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Revel in the exquisite detail of our world-renowned Mar-a-Lago Club, a National Historic Landmark and architectural icon in lavish Palm Beach. 📷: @courtlynnreed

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Trump Organization in Trump International Hotel Las Vegas with @trumphotels, and @trumplasvegas. May be an image of palm trees, outdoors and text that says 'TRUMP INTERNATIONAL T'.

node.text: Experience Las Vegas in style with @trumphotels #NeverSettleOffer, featuring an iconic Strip View room upgrade, poolside margaritas, a selection of warm weather amenities, and more. Book at the link in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Trump Organization in Trump National Golf Club Bedminster with @trumpgolf, and @trumpgolfbedminster. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Pairing world-class dining with spectacular views from the Orchid Room at @trumpgolfbedminster.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Trump Organization in Trump International Doonbeg with @trumphotels, @trumpdoonbeg, and @trumpgolf. May be an image of coast, nature and ocean.

node.text: In celebration of our 19th anniversary, discover the rich history behind the creation of one of Ireland’s most award-winning golf courses, @trumpdoonbeg. Read the story on the World of Trump blog at the link in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by The Trump Organization on July 07, 2021 tagging @trumphotels, and @albemarleestate. May be an image of tree and grass.

node.text: Virginia wine country awaits. Enjoy a dazzling stay at the exquisite Albemarle Estate with @trumphotels #NeverSettleOffer, featuring a luxury picnic for two, welcome cocktail, and more. Book at the link in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by The Trump Organization on July 07, 2021 tagging @trumphotels, and @albemarleestate. May be an image of tree and grass.
Photo by The Trump Organization on July 07, 2021. May be an image of nature.
Photo by The Trump Organization in Trump International Hotel Washington, D.C. with @trumphotels, and @trumpwashingtondc. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Celebrating 245 years of our great nation on this very special day in history. Happy Independence Day to all!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Trump Organization in Trump Golf Links Ferry Point with @michaelbreed, @trumpgolf, and @trumpgolfferrypoint. May be an image of golf course, grass and nature.

node.text: We are thrilled to announce that @trumpgolfferrypoint has been awarded by Northeast Golf Magazine as the #2 Best Public Course with the #1 Best Instructor, @michaelbreed, in the state of New York! Visit the link in our bio to learn more on The World of Trump Blog.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Trump Organization in Trump International Hotel & Tower Chicago with @trumphotels, and @trumpchicago. May be an image of skyscraper.

node.text: There’s nothing quite like summer in Chicago. Experience the city’s most special season with @trumphotels #NeverSettleOffer, featuring 2 tickets for Wendella's architectural boat cruise, a dining credit, and a summer-themed welcome amenity. Book at the link in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by The Trump Organization on June 25, 2021 tagging @trumpturnberryscotland, and @maple.thetoypoodle. May be an image of monument and outdoors.

node.text: The iconic @trumpturnberryscotland boasts championship golf, stunning coastline views, and the cutest pups around. 📷: @maple.thetoypoodle #NationalTakeYourDogToWorkDay
